By Gabriel Ogunjobi  Singer and songwriter, Adekunle Gold is happy that he has his music projects sorted for the next three years. He expressed excitement about this on Twitter handle on Tuesday. He tweeted: “God needs to forgive me for the times that I feared that I might run out of amazing music and things to say. Look at me, I have 2020, 2021, 2022 projects sorted!’ In September, Gold released his latest single entitled “Young Love,” his fifth record for the year. The record followed his widely accepted ‘Kelegbe Megbe’ hit song.